<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-find-combination-therapy-reduces-effects-of-zombie-cells-in-diabetic-kidney-disease/">Mayo Clinic researchers find combination therapy reduces effects of &amp;#8216;zombie cells&amp;#8217; in diabetic kidney disease</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
