		<title>Tomorrow&amp;#8217;s Cure: The quiet beginnings of leukemia</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/tomorrows-cure-the-quiet-beginnings-of-leukemia/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[jftmayo]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 13:26:13 +0000</pubDate>
